    <item>
      <title>前特朗普助手为拉丁美洲寻找中东投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/former-trump-aide-seeks-middle-east-investors-for-latin-america</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的一位前顾问正在努力将中东私募股权投资引入拉丁美洲，并聘请一位长期担任厄瓜多尔外交官来牵头筹建一只基金，并利用候任总统重返总统的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/former-trump-aide-seeks-middle-east-investors-for-latin-america</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币暴跌：特朗普的兴奋让位于美联储的谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-fed-wariness-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bitwise Asset Management 首席信息官 Matt Hougan 告诉 Caroline Hyde，他认为加密货币和比特币在过去几天的疲软是“健康回调”，不会影响该资产类别今年的整体强劲表现。他在“彭博科技”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-fed-wariness-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 20:16:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普惊叹科技巨头的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/trump-marvels-at-tech-titans-attention-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技行业最有影响力的领导者正在尝试一种新策略来吸引唐纳德·特朗普，后者历来反对他们的主导地位：面对面用餐。彭博社的库尔特·瓦格纳 (Kurt Wagner) 与卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 一起参加“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/trump-marvels-at-tech-titans-attention-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 20:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>礼来在 Novo 受挫后巩固减肥领域领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/healthcare-equity-strategist-on-novo-setback-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[减肥药制造商之间的激烈竞争导致华尔街的期望值过高，投资者期待新药的功效逐渐增强，服用起来也更加容易。现在，该行业可能已经触及天花板，一些专家表示，投资者对不断增加的减肥效果的痴迷可能是错误的。瑞穗的 Jared Holz 在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/healthcare-equity-strategist-on-novo-setback-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 19:41:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新民主党撤回支持 特鲁多政府面临垮台风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多的一位前重要盟友表示，他将投票推翻政府，此举可能会导致加拿大在明年初陷入选举，除非总理寻求暂时中止议会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储与特朗普的贸易战推动美元创下 2016 年以来最佳季度表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-trump-trade-drives-dollar-to-best-quarter-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元有望迎来 2022 年以来最好的一个季度，由于美国经济的韧性和美联储的鹰派前景增强了其吸引力，美元本周攀升至两年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-trump-trade-drives-dollar-to-best-quarter-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储关键通胀数据落后于预期，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于备受关注的一批通胀数据低于预期，导致交易员上调对美联储明年降息的预期，美国国债周五晚些时候脱离盘中高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险和美联储放缓宽松步伐导致油价周线下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡美联储降息步伐放缓以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对欧盟国家征收关税（除非它们购买更多美国石油和天然气），原油价格本周出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要：股市将迎来一个月以来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储决定明年降息时更加谨慎，市场因此动荡，美国主要股指本周有望创下 11 月中旬以来最糟糕的一周。美国国债连续第二周遭遇抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
